<i>noun</i>: 폭락 [퐁낙], 추락 [추락], 조락 [조락] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>폭락 [퐁낙]</dt><br>
<dd>1. plunge; nosedive</dd><br>
<dd>물건의 값이나 주가 등이 갑자기 크게 떨어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of the price of goods, stocks, etc., decreasing drastically and quickly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. collapse; falling</dd><br>
<dd>인기나 체면 등이 갑자기 매우 심하게 떨어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's popularity, dignity, etc., falling suddenly and dramatically.</dd><br>
<dt>추락 [추락]</dt><br>
<dd>1. falling; dropping; plunging</dd><br>
<dd>높은 곳에서 떨어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of falling from a high place.</dd><br>
<dd>2. loss; falling; damage</dd><br>
<dd>권위, 체면, 가치 등이 떨어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The fall of prestige, honor, value, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>조락 [조락]</dt><br>
<dd>1. falling</dd><br>
<dd>풀잎이나 나뭇잎 등이 시들어 떨어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of grass or leaves withering and falling.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fall; demise</dd><br>
<dd>점점 약해져 보잘것없이 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of growing weaker and shabby.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>